  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*quantum determinant*)\nClearAll[qdetT];\nqdetT[λ1_,λ2_][u_]:=T[λ1,λ2][1,1][u].T[λ1,λ2][2,2][u-h]-T[λ1,λ2][2,1][u].T[λ1,λ2][1,2][u-h];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Fusion/Hirota hierarchy for the two-site transfer matrices t2[λ1,λ2][1,s][u], built exactly as in the L=1 case (t2[λ1,λ2][2,1][u]=χ2 qdetT[λ1,λ2][u], then Hirota recursion t2[1,s][u]=t2[1,s-1][u].t2[1,1][u+(s-1)h]-t2[2,1][u+(s-1)h].t2[1,s-2][u]), with boundary conditions t2[0,s]=t2[a,0]=identity on V_λ1⊗V_λ2.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*fused transfer matrices*)\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][0,s_][u_]:=IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ1,0}]*dim[{λ2,0}]];\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][a_,0][u_]:=IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ1,0}]*dim[{λ2,0}]];\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][2,1][u_]:=χ2 qdetT[λ1,λ2][u];\nt2[λ1_,λ2_][1,s_/;s>1][u_]:=t2[λ1,λ2][1,s-1][u].t2[λ1,λ2][1,1][u+(s-1)h]-t2[λ1,λ2][2,1][u+(s-1)h].t2[λ1,λ2][1,s-2][u];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Qθ-type factors for the two sites*)\nClearAll[Qθ1,Qθ];\nQθ1[u_]:=(u-θ1);\nQθ[u_]:=(u-θ1)(u-θ2);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*SoV B-operator for L=2: the bare (1,1) monodromy element (no G, no trace) — same convention as B[λ][u]=L[λ][1,1][u-θ] at L=1.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[B2];\nB2[λ1_,λ2_][u_]:=T[λ1,λ2][1,1][u];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Step 8: SoV pseudovacuum for L=2 as the tensor product of the two single-site lowest-weight covectors.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Yangian weight eigenvalue of T[1,1] on HWS*)\nClearAll[ν1];\nν1[λ1_,λ2_][u_]:=(u-θ1- h λ1)(u-θ2-h λ2);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[xSingle,x2];\nxSingle[λ_][{0}]:={Table[KroneckerDelta[ii,dim[{λ,0}]],{ii,1,dim[{λ,0}]}]};\nx2[λ1_,λ2_][{0,0}]:=KroneckerProduct[xSingle[λ1][{0}],xSingle[λ2][{0}]];\n\nx2[λ1_,λ2_][{s1_,s2_}] := x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,s2}] = x2[λ1,λ2][{0,0}].t2[λ1,λ2][1,s1][θ1].t2[λ1,λ2][1,s2][θ2]/(Product[ν1[λ1,λ2][θ1 + (k - 1) h], {k, 1, s1}] Product[ν1[λ1,λ2][θ2 + (k - 1) h], {k, 1, s2}]);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "x2[2,1][{2,0}]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"568\" data-out-n=\"52\" data-sub-idx=\"0\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"26\" data-sub-start=\"0\" data-sub-end=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[52]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj4xbm-rdpv9q7\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"XGJlZ2lue3BtYXRyaXh9MCAmIFxmcmFjezF9ezJ9ICYgMCAmIDAgJiAwICYgMFxlbmR7cG1hdHJpeH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2051em;vertical-align:-0.3526em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mtable\"><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8526em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.0074em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3526em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8526em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.0074em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8451em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.655em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.394em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.345em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3526em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8526em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.0074em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3526em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8526em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.0074em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3526em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8526em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.0074em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3526em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8526em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.0074em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3526em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
