       "data": "Out[190]= \\sqrt[3]{k}\\,\\left(\\left(-1.18561270626131985872+0.832253303224995280404\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k^2-\\left(0.761819910806671651081+0.812812473459294825632\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k-\\left(0.404410037536507329420+0.598870869485872613792\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\right)",
