  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Mirrored statement: localizing to site 2 by cancelling site 1's tower. By the θ1<->θ2, λ1<->λ2\nsymmetry of mu[λ1,λ2][2][u] = Nn[λ1,λ2][2]/(Product_{k=0}^{λ1}(u-θ1-hk)Product_{k=0}^{λ2}(u-θ2-hk))\n(1-Exp[2πi/h(u-θ1)]), the same argument with the roles of the two sites swapped predicts\nP2site1[λ1][u] = Product_{k=0}^{λ1}(u-θ1-hk) cancels site 1's tower, and\nC2pred[λ1,λ2] = (-1)^(λ1-1) Product_{k=0}^{λ1}(θ1+kh-θ2).\nThis also requires building the SITE-2 analogue of Section F's 1-site machinery (Nn1s2/mu1s2/br1s2/det1s2,\nnormalized so the leading θ2-node weight is 1, exactly parallel to Nn1/mu1/br1/det1) since there is no\nexisting standalone single-site-at-θ2 construction in the notebook (Section E's xL1/t1 use θ1 only).*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Site-2 mirror of P1site2/C1pred.*)\nClearAll[P2site1,C2pred];\nP2site1[λ1_][u_] := Product[(u-θ1-h k),{k,0,λ1}];\nC2pred[λ1_,λ2_] := (-1)^(λ1-1) Product[(θ1+k h-θ2),{k,0,λ1}];\n\n(*Site-2 analogue of Nn1/mu1/br1/det1 (Section F), built around θ2 instead of θ1 — same\n  construction, just re-centered, so that det1s2[λ2][f] is the genuine 1-site-at-θ2 FSoV determinant.*)\nClearAll[Nn1s2,mu1s2,br1s2,det1s2];\nNn1s2[λ_] := Nn1s2[λ] = Module[{uu}, 1/(2 π I Residue[1/Product[(uu-θ2-h k),{k,0,λ}],{uu,θ2}])];\nmu1s2[λ_][u_] := Nn1s2[λ]/Product[(u-θ2-h k),{k,0,λ}];\nbr1s2[λ_][f_] := 2 π I Plus@@(Residue[f mu1s2[λ][u],{u,#}]&/@Table[θ2+h k,{k,0,λ}]);\ndet1s2[λ_][f_] := br1s2[λ][f]/(f/.u->θ2);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Sanity: Nn1s2 normalization gives leading (θ2-node) weight 1, and br1s2[λ][1]=0, mirroring\n  Cell 65's Nn1Check for the θ1 construction.*)\nClearAll[Nn1s2Check];\nNn1s2Check = Table[\n  w0 = 2 π I Residue[mu1s2[λ][u],{u,θ2}] // Simplify;\n  {λ, w0, br1s2[λ][1]//Simplify}\n,{λ,1,3}];\nIf[Union[Nn1s2Check[[All,2]]] =!= {1} || Union[Nn1s2Check[[All,3]]] =!= {0}, Abort[]];\nNn1s2Check",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"608\" data-out-n=\"271\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"84\" data-sub-start=\"8\" data-sub-end=\"8\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[271]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj6kmu-7lx5j23\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"XGJlZ2lue3BtYXRyaXh9MSAmIDEgJiAwXFwyICYgMSAmIDBcXDMgJiAxICYgMFxlbmR7cG1hdHJpeH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:3.6em;vertical-align:-1.55em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.6em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:3.600em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"3.600em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 3600\"><path d=\"M863,9c0,-2,-2,-5,-6,-9c0,0,-17,0,-17,0c-12.7,0,-19.3,0.3,-20,1\nc-5.3,5.3,-10.3,11,-15,17c-242.7,294.7,-395.3,682,-458,1162c-21.3,163.3,-33.3,349,\n-36,557 l0,84c0.2,6,0,26,0,60c2,159.3,10,310.7,24,454c53.3,528,210,\n949.7,470,1265c4.7,6,9.7,11.7,15,17c0.7,0.7,7,1,19,1c0,0,18,0,18,0c4,-4,6,-7,6,-9\nc0,-2.7,-3.3,-8.7,-10,-18c-135.3,-192.7,-235.5,-414.3,-300.5,-665c-65,-250.7,-102.5,\n-544.7,-112.5,-882c-2,-104,-3,-167,-3,-189\nl0,-92c0,-162.7,5.7,-314,17,-454c20.7,-272,63.7,-513,129,-723c65.3,\n-210,155.3,-396.3,270,-559c6.7,-9.3,10,-15.3,10,-18z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.55em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mtable\"><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.21em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.01em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-1.81em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">3</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.55em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.21em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.01em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-1.81em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.55em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.21em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.01em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-1.81em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.55em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.6em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:3.600em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"3.600em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 3600\"><path d=\"M76,0c-16.7,0,-25,3,-25,9c0,2,2,6.3,6,13c21.3,28.7,42.3,60.3,\n63,95c96.7,156.7,172.8,332.5,228.5,527.5c55.7,195,92.8,416.5,111.5,664.5\nc11.3,139.3,17,290.7,17,454c0,28,1.7,43,3.3,45l0,9\nc-3,4,-3.3,16.7,-3.3,38c0,162,-5.7,313.7,-17,455c-18.7,248,-55.8,469.3,-111.5,664\nc-55.7,194.7,-131.8,370.3,-228.5,527c-20.7,34.7,-41.7,66.3,-63,95c-2,3.3,-4,7,-6,11\nc0,7.3,5.7,11,17,11c0,0,11,0,11,0c9.3,0,14.3,-0.3,15,-1c5.3,-5.3,10.3,-11,15,-17\nc242.7,-294.7,395.3,-681.7,458,-1161c21.3,-164.7,33.3,-350.7,36,-558\nl0,-144c-2,-159.3,-10,-310.7,-24,-454c-53.3,-528,-210,-949.7,\n-470,-1265c-4.7,-6,-9.7,-11.7,-15,-17c-0.7,-0.7,-6.7,-1,-18,-1z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.55em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
