  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Quick structural check before building more elaborate candidates: does O2rot factorize as a\n  plain product of its two 1-parameter slices, O[k1,k2] =? O[k1,0]*O[0,k2] (would hold iff Psi\n  were literally a product state under this rotation action — generically false for an entangled\n  two-site eigenstate, but cheap to rule out first).*)\nOfact = Simplify[Oc1 - (O2rot[2,1][1,0][k1,0] O2rot[2,1][1,0][0,k2])];\nChop[N[Ofact],10^-12]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"618\" data-out-n=\"318\" data-sub-idx=\"2\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"97\" data-sub-start=\"5\" data-sub-end=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[318]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj6sri-q2e18mf\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnQoMC45MjUyMTI1MDM0ODk5ODg44oCKLTYuMTc1NzI3NTA4NzY1NDQzXCxcbWF0aHJte2l9XHJpZ2h0KVwsazFeMlwsazIrXGxlZnQoNS40MjcxMjY3NDgyMjkxMDc14oCKKzMuMDg5MDAwNDM2Njc3MzA2N1wsXG1hdGhybXtpfVxyaWdodClcLGsxXCxrMg==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.1141em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">0.9252125034899888 </span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">6.175727508765443</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.11