      {
       "data": "Out[343]= \\left\\{\\text{Fcand1(k1,0)},\\left(-8.51191121729+7.73287575414\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1^2-\\left(4.5054984393+11.6597806074\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1+\\left(1.000000000000+0.\\times 10^{-12}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right),\\text{FLdet[k1]},\\frac{\\left(2.45075493251774917289426756629+5.78551794268217244227029022731\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,\\left(\\left(0.05259468771783351844996683714+0.15021349717800998891606886537\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1^{7/3}-\\left(0.31814747276780284588403220033+0.01016706515165109136900866395\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1^{4/3}+\\left(0.062078347644998994100866232323-0.146548881484135151702967504594\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,\\sqrt[3]{k1}\\right)}{\\sqrt[3]{k1}},\\text{ratio (want: k1-independent const)},\\frac{\\left(11.500+0.\\times 10^{-4}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1^2-\\left(4.5055-11.660\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1-\\left(0.74017+0.67242\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)}{{\\left(\\left(0.36044-0.93278\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)-\\left(1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-5}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1\\right)}^2}\\right\\}",
