       "data": "Out[354]= \\left\\{\\text{STEP 0 CONFIRMED: det[$\\lambda$1,$\\lambda$2][k\\^{}(u/h)Q1] == O[k,k] identically},\\text{worst residual over full sweep},0,\\text{num states},41\\right\\}",
