      {
       "data": "Out[404]= \\left\\{\\text{m=0: Om-Cm (must be 0 per Phase1, C1pred/P1site2[$\\theta$1] should equal exactly Cm's own norm here)},\\left(2.5572121404875445 -0.4102640568287387\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1-\\left(0.038411844228125346 +2.1227491621421546\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1^2,\\text{m=1: Om\\_1[k1]},\\left(0.3604398751472265372666776506+0.9327824485933747164848359821\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1^2-\\left(1.296101147801774460249890292+2.676661693287278344489306162\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1+\\left(2.603469709065218092712489006+0.6885776528619826437114966465\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right),\\text{m=1: Cm\\_1[k1]},\\left(0.02466179161444500699+1.36288164597304174980\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1^2-\\left(6.4691378554000385439-1.0378703818584163093\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k1+\\left(1.000000000000000000000+0.\\times 10^{-21}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\right\\}",
