  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Symbolic decomposition, θA,θB GENUINELY free (unlike θ1,θ2 which already carry numeric values —\n  see the fix note on the previous cell). Solve x2Sym[{s1,m}] = Σ A[s1,m;s1',m'] xL1Sym[λ1][{s1'}]\n  ⊗xL1Sym[λ2][{m'}] over the FULL basis (not assuming level-conservation — that should fall out of\n  the symbolic solve as A=0 off-level, reconfirming Section I's numeric finding analytically).\n  (*why no underscores in variable names*) Wolfram Language reserves \"_\" for pattern syntax even\n  mid-identifier (e.g. \"dCase1101\" not \"d11_01\") — a literal underscore in a variable name silently\n  turns it into a Blank pattern, causing Set::write errors on assignment.*)\nClearAll[fullBasisSym,decompX2Sym];\nfullBasisSym[λ1_,λ2_] := Flatten[Table[\n   {s1p,m1p} -> Flatten[KroneckerProduct[xL1Sym[θA][λ1][{s1p}], xL1Sym[θB][λ2][{m1p}]]]\n  ,{s1p,0,λ1},{m1p,0,λ2}], 1];\ndecompX2Sym[λ1_,λ2_][s1_,m_] := Module[{basisRules,basisVecs,mat,target,sol},\n  basisRules = fullBasisSym[λ1,λ2];\n  basisVecs = basisRules[[All,2]];\n  mat = Transpose[basisVecs];\n  target = Flatten[x2Sym[θA,θB][λ1,λ2][{s1,m}]];\n  sol = Simplify[LinearSolve[mat, target]];\n  Thread[basisRules[[All,1]] -> sol]\n];\n(*smallest nontrivial case first: λ1=1,λ2=1, state (s1,m)=(0,1) — should mix (0,1) and (1,0).*)\ndCase1101 = decompX2Sym[1,1][0,1];\ndCase1101",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"641\" data-out-n=\"451\" data-sub-idx=\"6\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"126\" data-sub-start=\"21\" data-sub-end=\"21\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[451]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj78qs-145juir\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1xsZWZ0XHswLDBccmlnaHRcfVx0byAwLFxsZWZ0XHswLDFccmlnaHRcfVx0byBcZnJhY3tcdGhldGEgQS1cdGhldGEgQn17XHRoZXRhIEEtXHRoZXRhIEIrMX0sXGxlZnRcezEsMFxyaWdodFx9XHRvIFxmcmFjezF9e1x0aGV0YSBBLVx0aGV0YSBCKzF9LFxsZWZ0XHsxLDFccmlnaHRcfVx0byAwXHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.4em;vertical-align:-0.95em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">{</span></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3714em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7693em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7693em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[451]= \\left\\{\\left\\{0,0\\right\\}\\to 0,\\left\\{0,1\\right\\}\\to \\frac{\\theta A-\\theta B}{\\theta A-\\theta B+1},\\left\\{1,0\\right\\}\\to \\frac{1}{\\theta A-\\theta B+1},\\left\\{1,1\\right\\}\\to 0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "86e81404-e3ba-448b-8324-523563e652e7"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Full symbolic sweep λ1,λ2∈{1,2}, all (s1,m). Collect every nonzero coefficient with its full\n  (λ1,λ2,s1,m,s1',m') label for pattern-hunting.*)\nsymSweep = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{d},\n        d = decompX2Sym[λ1,λ2][s1,m];\n        Do[\n          If[rule[[2]]=!=0, AppendTo[symSweep, {λ1,λ2,s1,m,rule[[1,1]],rule[[1,2]],rule[[2]]}]]\n        ,{rule,d}]\n      ]\n    ,{m,0,λ2}]\n  ,{s1,0,λ1}]\n,{λ1,{1,2}},{λ2,{1,2}}];\nLength[symSweep]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"642\" data-out-n=\"454\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"127\" data-sub-start=\"15\" data-sub-end=\"15\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[454]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj798a-hftgnye\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"MzU=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">35</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[454]= 35",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "f25d54e0-eb63-4be4-bd2f-02f1e06a8fec"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Rescale to the RAW (unnormalized) numerators — yL1 := xSingle.t1[1,s][θ] (no ν1Single division),\n  y2 := x2[{0,0}].t2[1,s1][θa].t2[1,m][θb] (no ν1Two division) — to see if the underlying recoupling\n  B is a clean combinatorial (Vandermonde-type) matrix once the known θ-dependent normalization\n  factors D1,D2 are stripped out.*)\nClearAll[yL1Sym,y2Sym,decompY2Sym];\nyL1Sym[θa_][λ_][{s_}] := xSingle[λ][{0}].t1Sym[θa][λ][1,s][θa];\ny2Sym[θa_,θb_][λ1_,λ2_][{s1_,s2_}] := x2Sym[θa,θb][λ1,λ2][{0,0}].t2Sym[θa,θb][λ1,λ2][1,s1][θa].t2Sym[θa,θb][λ1,λ2][1,s2][θb];\nfullBasisYSym[λ1_,λ2_] := Flatten[Table[\n   {s1p,m1p} -> Flatten[KroneckerProduct[yL1Sym[θA][λ1][{s1p}], yL1Sym[θB][λ2][{m1p}]]]\n  ,{s1p,0,λ1},{m1p,0,λ2}], 1];\ndecompY2Sym[λ1_,λ2_][s1_,m_] := Module[{basisRules,basisVecs,mat,target,sol},\n  basisRules = fullBasisYSym[λ1,λ2];\n  basisVecs = basisRules[[All,2]];\n  mat = Transpose[basisVecs];\n  target = Flatten[y2Sym[θA,θB][λ1,λ2][{s1,m}]];\n  sol = Simplify[LinearSolve[mat, target]];\n  Thread[basisRules[[All,1]] -> sol]\n];\n(*same smallest test case: λ1=1,λ2=1, (s1,m)=(0,1).*)\ndecompY2Sym[1,1][0,1]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"643\" data-out-n=\"460\" data-sub-idx=\"7\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"128\" data-sub-start=\"19\" data-sub-end=\"19\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[460]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj79j4-hx9mzo5\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1xsZWZ0XHswLDBccmlnaHRcfVx0byAwLFxsZWZ0XHswLDFccmlnaHRcfVx0byBcdGhldGEgQi1cdGhldGEgQSxcbGVmdFx7MSwwXHJpZ2h0XH1cdG8gLTEsXGxlZnRcezEsMVxyaWdodFx9XHRvIDBccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[460]= \\left\\{\\left\\{0,0\\right\\}\\to 0,\\left\\{0,1\\right\\}\\to \\theta B-\\theta A,\\left\\{1,0\\right\\}\\to -1,\\left\\{1,1\\right\\}\\to 0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "5c0aab38-4660-41a7-aac7-22cb2fb1ffe9"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Full B-sweep, λ1,λ2∈{1,2,3} (larger than before since B looks much cheaper/cleaner — polynomial,\n  not rational — so bigger reps should still be tractable).*)\nsymSweepB = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{d},\n        d = decompY2Sym[λ1,λ2][s1,m];\n        Do[\n          If[rule[[2]]=!=0, AppendTo[symSweepB, {λ1,λ2,s1,m,rule[[1,1]],rule[[1,2]],rule[[2]]}]]\n        ,{rule,d}]\n      ]\n    ,{m,0,λ2}]\n  ,{s1,0,λ1}]\n,{λ1,{1,2,3}},{λ2,{1,2,3}}];\nLength[symSweepB]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"644\" data-out-n=\"463\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"129\" data-sub-start=\"15\" data-sub-end=\"15\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[463]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj7asi-u1fwta4\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"MTI3\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">127</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[463]= 127",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "142cfbf7-1465-4701-9ed5-7acc52e9bf36"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Extend the clean A-sweep to λ1,λ2∈{1,2,3} (bug-fixed χ1sym version) — bigger than the earlier\n  λ≤2 sweep, to get more data for pattern-hunting; only keep diagonal + one-step-off-diagonal entries\n  to control runtime (LinearSolve over larger bases is the bottleneck for λ=3).*)\nsymSweepFull = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{d},\n        d = decompX2Sym[λ1,λ2][s1,m];\n        Do[\n          If[rule[[2]]=!=0, AppendTo[symSweepFull, {λ1,λ2,s1,m,rule[[1,1]],rule[[1,2]],Factor[rule[[2]]]}]]\n        ,{rule,d}]\n      ]\n    ,{m,0,λ2}]\n  ,{s1,0,λ1}]\n,{λ1,{1,2,3}},{λ2,{1,2,3}}];\nLength[symSweepFull]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"645\" data-out-n=\"466\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"130\" data-sub-start=\"16\" data-sub-end=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[466]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj7by5-jjyfwpa\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"MTI3\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">127</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[466]= 127",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "8f4da875-9c21-4367-922b-2355991b1fcf"
    }
