  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Full B-sweep, rationalized, all reps in the standard sweep — check (i) exact-0 residual always,\n  (ii) whether B[a,b;s,t] depends on λ2 (mirroring A's λ2-independence) or on both λ1,λ2.*)\nClearAll[solveBrat];\nsolveBrat[λ1_,λ2_][a_,b_] := Module[{L,srng,states,matEqs,rhsEqs,sol,resid},\n  L = a+b;\n  srng = Range[Max[0,L-λ2],Min[L,λ1]];\n  states = statesOf[λ1,λ2];\n  matEqs = Table[Wval[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]][s,L-s], {st,states},{s,srng}];\n  rhsEqs = Table[MPfun[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]][a,b], {st,states}];\n  sol = LeastSquares[matEqs, rhsEqs];\n  resid = Max[Abs[matEqs.sol - rhsEqs]];\n  {srng, Rationalize[Chop[sol,10^-15],10^-9], resid}\n];\nfullBsweep = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{res},\n        res = solveBrat[λ1,λ2][a,b];\n        AppendTo[fullBsweep, {λ1,λ2,a,b,res[[1]],res[[2]],res[[3]]}]\n      ]\n    ,{b,0,λ2}]\n  ,{a,0,λ1}]\n,{rep,{{2,1},{1,2},{3,1},{1,3},{2,2}}},{λ1,{rep[[1]]}},{λ2,{rep[[2]]}}];\nworstBresid = Max[fullBsweep[[All,7]]];\n{\"worst residual across full B-sweep (want ~0)\", worstBresid, \"num (rep,a,b) cases\", Length[fullBsweep]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"655\" data-out-n=\"521\" data-sub-idx=\"6\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"143\" data-sub-start=\"25\" data-sub-end=\"25\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[521]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj7n1i-lwon9fh\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e3dvcnN0IHJlc2lkdWFsIGFjcm9zcyBmdWxsIEItc3dlZXAgKHdhbnQgXHRleHRhc2NpaXRpbGRle30wKX0sMC5cdGltZXMgMTBeey0yNH0sXHRleHR7bnVtIChyZXAsYSxiKSBjYXNlc30sMzdccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">worst residual across full B-sweep (want ~</span><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">24</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">num (rep,a,b) cases</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">37</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
