  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*STEP 4 — DERIVE (not guess) the sum rule, by expanding det[λ1,λ2][k^(u/h)Q1] as an explicit\nresidue sum. br[λ1,λ2][i][f]=Σ_s wi(s) f(θi+sh) (mu's poles are simple, so Residue[f·mu,pole] =\nf(pole)·Res[mu,pole] exactly — no derivatives needed), wi(s):=2πi Residue[mu[λ1,λ2][i][u],θi+sh].\nSubstituting into det's {f,uf} 2×2 Wronskian structure and simplifying the resulting determinant of\nsums (the (θ2+s2h)-(θ1+s1h) factor falls out of Det[{{f,uf}}] applied termwise) gives\n  det[λ1,λ2][k^(u/h)Q1] = Σ_{s1,s2} w1(s1)w2(s2)(θ2-θ1+(s2-s1)h)/(θ2-θ1) · k^(s1+s2) · W[s1,s2]\nusing STEP 1's W[s1,s2]=Q1(θ1+s1h)Q1(θ2+s2h)/(Q1(θ1)Q1(θ2))=x2[{s1,s2}].Psi. Comparing this\nQ-bilinear expansion of O[k,k] against STEP 3's assembly (Σ_L(-k)^L Σ_{s+t=L}W[s,t]Σ_{a+b=L}\nB[a,b;s,t]γ_a(λ1)γ_b(λ2)/(a!b!)) term-by-term in k^L·W[s,t] gives the TRUE sum rule:\n  (-1)^(s+t) Σ_{a+b=s+t} γ_a(λ1)γ_b(λ2)/(a!b!)·B[a,b;s,t] = w1(s)w2(t)(θ2-θ1+(t-s)h)/(θ2-θ1)*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*w1(s1),w2(s2): the ALREADY-KNOWN measure residue weights from Section C's mu[λ1,λ2][i][u].*)\nClearAll[w1wt,w2wt];\nw1wt[λ1_,λ2_][s1_] := 2 π I Residue[mu[λ1,λ2][1][u],{u,θ1+s1 h}];\nw2wt[λ1_,λ2_][s2_] := 2 π I Residue[mu[λ1,λ2][2][u],{u,θ2+s2 h}];\n(*Verify the STEP-4 derivation directly: does Σ_{s1,s2} w1(s1)w2(s2)(θ2-θ1+(s2-s1)h)/(θ2-θ1) k^(s1+s2) W[s1,s2]\n  reproduce det[λ1,λ2][k^(u/h)Q1] exactly, for a representative state?*)\nClearAll[detExpandedCheck];\ndetExpandedCheck[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][k_] := Sum[\n  w1wt[λ1,λ2][s1] w2wt[λ1,λ2][s2] (θ2-θ1+(s2-s1)h)/(θ2-θ1) k^(s1+s2) Wval[λ1,λ2][M,n][s1,s2]\n,{s1,0,λ1},{s2,0,λ2}];\ntestDetExpand = Simplify[\n  det[2,1][k^(u/h) Q1[2,1][1,0][u]] - detExpandedCheck[2,1][1,0][k]\n];\n{\"det[λ1,λ2][k^u Q1] - explicit residue-sum expansion (rep (2,1), state (1,0)), want 0\", Chop[N[testDetExpand]/.k->N[7/3+I/5],10^-10]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"657\" data-out-n=\"532\" data-sub-idx=\"8\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"146\" data-sub-start=\"13\" data-sub-end=\"13\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[532]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj7nvl-zb0xi71\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e2RldFskXGxhbWJkYSQxLCRcbGFtYmRhJDJdW2tcXnt9dSBRMV0gLSBleHBsaWNpdCByZXNpZHVlLXN1bSBleHBhbnNpb24gKHJlcCAoMiwxKSwgc3RhdGUgKDEsMCkpLCB3YW50IDB9LDBccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">det[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">1,</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">2][k</span><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"accent-body\" style=\"left:-0.25em;\"><span class=\"mord\">ˆ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\">u Q1] - explicit residue-sum expansion (rep (2,1), state (1,0)), want 0</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[532]= \\left\\{\\text{det[$\\lambda$1,$\\lambda$2][k\\^{}u Q1] - explicit residue-sum expansion (rep (2,1), state (1,0)), want 0},0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "0f2a6e9b-ba84-44ae-b63e-ae6f27bef1bf"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Hard-verify the DERIVED sum rule:\n     (-1)^(s+t) Σ_{a+b=s+t} γ_a(λ1)γ_b(λ2)/(a!b!)·B[a,b;s,t] = w1(s)w2(t)(θ2-θ1+(t-s)h)/(θ2-θ1)\n   using the rationalized B entries already solved (solveBrat) and the closed-form γ_a(λ)=λ!/(λ-a)!.\n   (*why the a-range fix*) the sum over a must respect 0<=a<=λ1 AND 0<=L-a<=λ2 (xL1[λ][{a}] is\n   undefined outside 0..λ) — the unrestricted range hit invalid (a,b) pairs, producing\n   Power::infy/Indeterminate from a malformed solveBrat call.*)\nClearAll[gammaFun];\ngammaFun[λ_,a_] := λ!/(λ-a)!;\nsumRuleTrue = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{L,lhs,rhs,aMin,aMax},\n        L = s+t;\n        aMin = Max[0,L-λ2]; aMax = Min[L,λ1];\n        lhs = (-1)^L Sum[\n          Module[{bv,srng},\n            {srng,bv} = solveBrat[λ1,λ2][a,L-a][[1;;2]];\n            If[MemberQ[srng,s], gammaFun[λ1,a] gammaFun[λ2,L-a]/(a!(L-a)!) bv[[Position[srng,s][[1,1]]]], 0]\n          ]\n        ,{a,aMin,aMax}];\n        rhs = w1wt[λ1,λ2][s] w2wt[λ1,λ2][t] (θ2-θ1+(t-s)h)/(θ2-θ1);\n        AppendTo[sumRuleTrue, {λ1,λ2,s,t, Chop[N[lhs-rhs],10^-8]}]\n      ]\n    ,{t,0,λ2}]\n  ,{s,0,λ1}]\n,{rep,{{2,1},{1,2},{3,1}}},{λ1,{rep[[1]]}},{λ2,{rep[[2]]}}];\nworstSumRuleTrue = Max[Abs[sumRuleTrue[[All,5]]]];\n{\"TRUE sum rule (derived, Step 4): worst deviation\", worstSumRuleTrue, \"num (λ1,λ2,s,t) cases\", Length[sumRuleTrue],\n \"sample\", Take[sumRuleTrue,UpTo[6]]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941591\" data-output-id=\"658\" data-out-n=\"538\" data-sub-idx=\"6\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"147\" data-sub-start=\"28\" data-sub-end=\"29\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[538]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqj7och-pbt5qpu\" data-page-width-em=\"23\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:7.2001em;vertical-align:-3.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:3.85em;\"><span style=\"top:-1.366em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.816em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎩</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-1.358em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.816em;\"></span><span style=\"height:1.816em;width:0.8889em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.8889em\" height=\"1.816em\" style=\"width:0.8889em\" viewBox=\"0 0 888.89 1816\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin\"><path d=\"M384 0 H504 V1816 H384z M384 0 H504 V1816 H384z\"/></svg></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.816em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.816em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎨</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-4.958em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.816em;\"></span><span style=\"height:1.816em;width:0.8889em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.8889em\" height=\"1.816em\" style=\"width:0.8889em\" viewBox=\"0 0 888.89 1816\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin\"><path d=\"M384 0 H504 V1816 H384z M384 0 H504 V1816 H384z\"/></svg></span></span><span style=\"top:-6.766em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.816em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎧</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:3.35em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">TRUE sum rule (derived, Step 4): worst deviation</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">num (</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">1,</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">2,s,t) cases</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">20</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">sample</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:3.85em;\"><span style=\"top:-5.8499em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:9.2em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:7.200em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"7.200em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 7200\"><path d=\"M863,9c0,-2,-2,-5,-6,-9c0,0,-17,0,-17,0c-12.7,0,-19.3,0.3,-20,1\nc-5.3,5.3,-10.3,11,-15,17c-242.7,294.7,-395.3,682,-458,1162c-21.3,163.3,-33.3,349,\n-36,557 l0,3684c0.2,6,0,26,0,60c2,159.3,10,310.7,24,454c53.3,528,210,\n949.7,470,1265c4.7,6,9.7,11.7,15,17c0.7,0.7,7,1,19,1c0,0,18,0,18,0c4,-4,6,-7,6,-9\nc0,-2.7,-3.3,-8.7,-10,-18c-135.3,-192.7,-235.5,-414.3,-300.5,-665c-65,-250.7,-102.5,\n-544.7,-112.5,-882c-2,-104,-3,-167,-3,-189\nl0,-3692c0,-162.7,5.7,-314,17,-454c20.7,-272,63.7,-513,129,-723c65.3,\n-210,155.3,-396.3,270,-559c6.7,-9.3,10,-15.3,10,-18z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:3.35em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mtable\"><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:3.85em;\"><span style=\"top:-6.01em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-4.81em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.61em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-2.41em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-1.21em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-0.01em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:3.35em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span cl